reviewText: Keeps my grandson moving on "stay inside days".  Exactly what I wanted.
This dvd production value is terrible and my kids could not get into this dvd at all I do not recommend this dvd.
great workout for adults and kids, fun sets and music and not too long.  my sister and her daughter loved it

I bought this video to do with my 2 and 3 year old. I have no time for the gym. I am loving it. I am able to get my workout during our day. My kids ask to do it again and again. Thank you! I bought a DVD for my sister for Christmas! SHe is going to love it. Karen Bagley Orlando, FL.
